.","url":"https://sqst.in/NiivF","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-28T20:20:11","source":"ScoutQuest"},{"id":"260125139397389","title":"Banks' LCR dipped in Q3 due to slow deposit growth and high funding needs; HDFC Bank's LCR fell to 116, Federal Bank to 124, and Union Bank to 123.6.\nCredit grew 14.5% while deposits rose 12.7% as banks liquidated SLR for credit growth; revised RBI norms to aid LCR management from April.","summary":"Banks' LCR dipped in Q3 due to slow deposit growth and high funding needs; HDFC Bank's LCR fell to 116, Federal Bank to 124, and Union Bank to 123.6.\nCredit grew 14.5% while deposits rose 12.7% as banks liquidated SLR for credit growth; revised RBI norms to aid LCR management from April.","url":"https://www.financialexpress.com/business/banking-finance/banks-liquidity-coverage-ratio-dips-on-slow-deposits-high-funding-needs/4119040/","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-25T21:03:00","source":"Financial Express"},{"id":"802867051837789184","title":"Union Bank of India faces a one-day nationwide strike on 27th Jan 2026.\nThe bank is preparing to ensure smooth operations; impact remains unknown.","summary":"Union Bank of India faces a one-day nationwide strike on 27th Jan 2026.\nThe bank is preparing to ensure smooth operations; impact remains unknown.","url":"https://sqst.in/99PGi","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-24T17:17:01","source":"ScoutQuest"},{"id":"452952","title":"Systematix's Nikhil Khandelwal foresees a tough 2026 for Indian equities due to weak growth, consumption pressure, and export challenges.\nHe favors PSU banks like SBI, Bank of Baroda, Union Bank for growth; highlights SFBs and metal recycling for strong potential.","summary":"Systematix's Nikhil Khandelwal foresees a tough 2026 for Indian equities due to weak growth, consumption pressure, and export challenges.\nHe favors PSU banks like SBI, Bank of Baroda, Union Bank for growth; highlights SFBs and metal recycling for strong potential.","url":"https://www.cnbctv18.co